Title: ya_get_dimension()

Source: R/ya_get_dimension.R
ya_get_dimension.Rd

Description: A function gathers information about BPstat domains located at "https://bpstat.bportugal.pt/data/v1/domains/?lang=" ("PT" or "EN")

Usage

ya_get_dimension(lang = "EN")

Arguments

lang

A string that represents the languages supported by BPstat API. Currently only uses "PT" or "EN". Defaults to "EN"

Value

A DT datatable in RStudio viewer pane

Examples

ya_get_dimension()
